This woman thought it would be a good idea to wear her nice white dress, go to the beach and take photos, but nature had other plans. In a video posted on Facebook, a woman can be seen sitting on a large rock close to the sea, getting ready for a few snaps that were to follow. As she gets ready to pose for the camera, she gets swept away by the waves that obviously came unexpectedly. Nature can be so cruel sometimes. Watch the sad video below: